{"tid":1652408,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊傾傾點解今日和理非咁少","createTime":"2019-10-13T16:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:48:30.000Z","uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2787efa9f5ba10dd1101b7a75d7a4ddb1c83ab97","tid":1652408,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係怪和理非唔出黎<br />\n佢地唔出黎實有原因<br />\n我地搵到呢啲原因再諗諗點拆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 文宣不足</span></strong><br />\n文宣不足係一定<br />\n好多街坊淨係睇連儂牆<br />\n但呢個禮拜既牆同10.1比真係差好遠<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>解決方法：全民文宣，補牆、補牆、補牆</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2) 太勇武唔敢出</span></strong><br />\n有d和理非拖埋小朋友同老人家出黎<br />\n你點叫佢地同防暴對恃呀<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">解決方法：一定要卑d佢地參與到既活動出黎</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非流程<br />\n 1. 商場摺紙<br />\n 2. 砌字俾人影相呃like<br />\n 3. 流動文宣<br />\n 4. 讓街坊感覺良好、帶物資<br />\n 5. 影相廣傳一兩個小時集氣大會<br />\n 6. 典型和理非/創意活動<br />\n 7. 散場前完成任務<br />\n 8. 或散場前給予和理非明確目標：哨、屌狗"},{"pid":"865879b7e83875ba0b1aad904f8319c890fe9655","tid":1652408,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"宣傳問題，同唔會連出兩日<br />\n<br />\n***（借位宣傳）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇一家<br />\n停止互屌</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1014七點遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要瘋狂ig fb whatsapp group叫人去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連登仔要再創造奇跡！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n練定英文口號，印埋英文文宣，可以嘅帶埋美國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位手足聽日見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">WE WANT FREEDOM AND FREEDOM IS WHAT WE WILL GET!!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"e11b29dc15a83262d0e8c1b3431e42783ee1953f","tid":1652408,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"「其實要大量集人靠既唔係TG 群叫人<br />\n係靠<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">FB 同地區文宣</span></strong>‼️<br />\n<br />\n仲要<span style=\"color: blue;\">比時間3-5日 去做文宣</span> 宣傳先會聚集到更多人<br />\n<br />\n10月1 賀佢老母 呢個口號已經係 9月頭叫到10月1 真係人人就出黎賀佢老母<br />\n<br />\n10月4 因爲蒙面法 所以先有甘多人出黎反抗<br />\n<br />\n其餘日子，沒目標，時間短，街坊要返工，湊仔女，已沒太多時間，所以人少難聚人」"},{"pid":"f1600a1983a37b79c88776126cc0358051b26569","tid":1652408,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87c669e43fda7f57da43606931b55b60043b2e3f","tid":1652408,"uid":68261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3218f54a69d664cd31df7e9f46fe4e01b44d28a7","tid":1652408,"uid":182860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"呢段時間好似係考試季節"},{"pid":"e4284d2ef5ab0ae032125f87e3ee6b97770aa601","tid":1652408,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}